# Implement PackReader

Streaming pack file parser.

## Interface

```typescript
interface PackReader {
  /**
   * Iterate entries in pack order
   */
  entries(): AsyncIterable<PackEntry>;

  /**
   * Get pack header info
   */
  getHeader(): Promise<PackHeader>;
}

interface PackEntry {
  id: ObjectId;
  type: ObjectType;
  isDelta: boolean;
  baseRef?: ObjectId | number;  // SHA-1 or offset
  rawContent: AsyncIterable<Uint8Array>;      // As stored in pack
  resolvedContent: AsyncIterable<Uint8Array>; // Delta applied if needed
}

interface PackHeader {
  version: number;
  objectCount: number;
}
```

## Parsing Strategy

1. **Stream-based**: Don't load entire pack into memory
2. **Forward-only for OFS_DELTA**: Resolve during iteration
3. **Two-pass for REF_DELTA thin packs**: May need index first

## Delta Resolution

```typescript
for await (const entry of reader.entries()) {
  if (entry.isDelta) {
    // resolvedContent applies delta automatically
    yield* entry.resolvedContent;
  } else {
    yield* entry.rawContent;
  }
}
```

