Update Repository interface and GitRepository to expose RawStoreWithDelta for GC access.

## Problem

Currently, createGitRepository creates a RawStoreWithDelta internally but doesn't expose it. The GCController requires access to RawStoreWithDelta to perform garbage collection.

## Proposed Solution

Add optional deltaStorage property to GitRepository:

```typescript
