## Metrics

- **Compression ratio** - Output size / input size
- **Encoding speed** (MB/s) - Delta creation throughput
- **Decoding speed** (MB/s) - Delta application throughput
- **Memory usage** - Peak memory during operation

## Comparisons

- VCS delta vs native git
- Different content types (text, binary, mixed)
- Various file sizes (1KB, 10KB, 100KB, 1MB, 10MB)

